prodNameC: 貝爾斯噙咯色原質/膽色素原合酶試劑（未滅菌）
ingredientsDesc:
1. Reagnet 2 x 350 mL. Sodium acetate 1 mol/L.
2. Reagent 1 x 175 mL. Acetic acid 1 mol/L
3. PBG microcolumns. 2 x 20. Contain a pre-weighted amount of a buffered anionic exchange resin.
5. ALA microcolumns. 2 x 20. Contain a pre-weighted amount of a buffered cationic exchange resin.
A. Reagent. 1 x 17 mL. Acetylacetone.
B1. Reagent. 2 for 50 mL. 4-Dimethylaminobenzaldehyde 6 mmol/L, after reconstitution.
B2. Reagent 2 x 100 mL. Acetic acid 18 mol/L.
S. ALA Standard. 2 for 5 mL. Concentration of reconstituted standards is given on the label.
applicantAddr: 新北市板橋區民生路三段299巷13號4樓
efficacy: 測量五氨四酮-戊酸和紫質膽質原濃度用試劑。
